{"tid":416421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母呢個世界公平咩","createTime":"2017-09-27T18:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T19:06:05.000Z","uid":14549,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"095f82ab08ac63ac2b836cceac6de7980a9c6f1e","tid":416421,"uid":14549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"我問你 你鐘意你個ex啲咩<br />\n你答我 佢係你最無助既時候陪你<br />\n屌你老母臭閪<br />\n你最撚唔開心嗰陣我日撚日陪住你<br />\n全日咩都唔撚做就係陪你傾電話<br />\n眼訓都頂住等你訓左我先敢訓<br />\n點撚解你可以話佢係你最無助既時候陪住你<br />\n有冇諗撚過我感受呀屌你老母<br />\n到好返小小就去溝仔<br />\n比人飛就黎搵我傾？<br />\n咁都唔緊要<br />\n我心情唔撚好都要比說話我聽<br />\n我唔撚係人？<br />\n講到自己幾慘幾慘<br />\n全部都係自己拎黎<br />\n專揀埋啲賤男<br />\n比人飛就哭哭找媽媽<br />\n個撚個女人都係咁"},{"pid":"b7a1a81eec26bfc5864ac328514545d27361c078","tid":416421,"uid":8345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6fb5ef13928ca0315be7fd704c0b7d9cbb7b921","tid":416421,"uid":70425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:11:49.000Z","msg":"收皮啦垃圾"},{"pid":"38584380d714a524d79bf14ba4a8952e8ea43c53","tid":416421,"uid":14549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:12:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"afa1b7838a468fe3ad331a350962c010774b47ac","tid":416421,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哎呀有人做左水泡</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb8d5b307b0fc90507e6a78deeccf80c5f34640","tid":416421,"uid":74172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:16:24.000Z","msg":"樣子問題 身高問題.jpg"},{"pid":"f27bd4ddabf56070b5510a2db52686418c4d32f0","tid":416421,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"兵"},{"pid":"17b828319cf2e00b2cd4b9497cfbeac15c31a6f9","tid":416421,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"屌鳩佢，<br />\n然後